channel.title: JS5 error after working once or twice?!
channel.description: So basically... i run my server, open the client and go to log in... And it works... but then when i close it or restart my computer... When i run my server, and open my client i have a JS5 error. But my server is still online, just wont let anyone log in for some reason... help please. This is a 562 server
